LoessFunc <- function(SiteFilter,DF,SpanConstant = .163,Var){
  MainDF <- DF%>%
    filter(Site==SiteFilter)
  MainDF[[paste0("loess",Var)]] <- loessFit(y=(MainDF[[Var]]),
                      x=MainDF$Date, #create loess fit of the data
                      span=SpanConstant, #span of .2 seems to give the best result,
                                          #not rigorously chosen
                      iterations=5)$fitted#2 iterations remove some bad patterns
  #Same as above but for N2
  N2Name <- gsub("1","2",Var)
  MainDF[[paste0("loess", N2Name)]] <- loessFit(y=(MainDF[[N2Name]]),
                      x=MainDF$Date,
                      span=SpanConstant,
                      iterations=5)$fitted#
return(MainDF)
}

SiteLoessDF <- IntercepterDF%>%
  mutate(FlowN1 = FlowRate*N1,
         PopN1 = N1/Pop,
         FlowN2 = FlowRate*N2,
         PopN2 = N1/Pop)
  
  
  

BaseColDF <- lapply(c("MMSD-P11","MMSD-P18","MMSD-P2","MMSD-P7","MMSD-P8"),
                      LoessFunc,SiteLoessDF,SpanConstant = .15,
         Var = "N1")%>%
          bind_rows()%>%
        mutate(Norm = "None",
         CovConcNorm = loessN1,
         CovConcNorm2 = loessN2)

FlowColDF <- lapply(c("MMSD-P11","MMSD-P18","MMSD-P2","MMSD-P7","MMSD-P8"),
                      LoessFunc,SiteLoessDF,SpanConstant = .15,
         Var = "FlowN1")%>%
                bind_rows()%>%
  mutate(Norm = "Flow",
         CovConcNorm = loessFlowN1,
         CovConcNorm2 = loessFlowN2)

PopColDF <- lapply(c("MMSD-P11","MMSD-P18","MMSD-P2","MMSD-P7","MMSD-P8"),
                      LoessFunc,SiteLoessDF,SpanConstant = .15,
         Var = "PopN1")%>%
  bind_rows()%>%
  mutate(Norm = "Pop",
         CovConcNorm = loessPopN1,
         CovConcNorm2 = loessPopN2)


MergedToBeFacetedDF <- rbind(BaseColDF, FlowColDF, PopColDF)%>%
  mutate(Norm = factor(Norm,c("None","Flow","Pop")))%>%
  select(Norm,CovConcNorm,CovConcNorm2,Date)


BaseGridPlot <- MergedToBeFacetedDF%>%
            filter(!is.na(CovConcNorm))%>%                    
            ggplot(aes(x=Date))+
            geom_line(aes(y=CovConcNorm, color = Site, linetype  = "N1"))+
            geom_line(aes(y=CovConcNorm2, color = Site, linetype  = "N2"))+
            scale_colour_manual(values = HueSpace)+
            theme_light() +
            facet_wrap(~Norm, scales = "free_y",nrow=3) + 
              theme(panel.spacing = unit(2, "lines"))+
  ylab("gene concentration with Normalization (GC/L)")
            


NonLogPlotlyPlot <- BaseGridPlot+
            labs(title = "Linear scale", ylab = "Covid Conc With Norm")

LogPlotlyPlot <- BaseGridPlot+
            scale_y_log10()+
            labs(title = "Log scale")+
  theme(axis.title.y=element_blank())
